GIGOLO...THE....
He is available for a price
With various services
Ranging from chauperoning
To getting laid in gusto
With various postures
And sublime happiness
Leading to orgasms
For the dames without
The nuptial pleasures
Unsatisfied so far,
Costly he is, handsome hunk
He is to the look pleasures
And to be boasted
By the women's circle,
He lives a life of sexual
Attainment both for him
And rich luxurious buyers
Of his expensive services.
Ravikiran  Arakkal

